_:Nb9728d5c37ac41d4be9f6b8edaf4e70f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jane Ellison served as Financial Secretary to the Treasury from July 2016 until June 2017. Previously she was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Public Health at the Department of Health from October 2013 until July 2016.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected Conservative MP for Battersea in 2010.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
